      <h2>Registration Process Statement</h2> <br>
      <p>
        Welcome to HOMEHUB AGENCY, your premier platform for connecting landlords and house owners with tenants and buyers of properties 
        and landed properties. Before you begin using our services, we want to ensure that you understand our registration process and 
        the terms and conditions that govern your use of our application. Please read the following information carefully to complete 
        your registration successfully.</p> <br>
      <div class="card-content">

        <h3>1. Registration Process</h3>
        <p>Sign-Up: To register on our platform, please click on the "Sign Up" button on our homepage. You will be directed to a registration 
            form where you will need to provide your personal details such as your name, email address, phone number, and password.
        </p><br>

        <h3>2. Agreement Acceptance</h3>
        <p>Before completing your registration, you will be required to read and accept our Terms and Conditions, Service Fee Agreement, 
            and Privacy Policy. These documents outline the rules, fees, and privacy practices that govern your use of our application.
        </p>
        <br>

        <h3>3. Verification</h3>
        <p>After submitting your registration details and accepting the agreements, you will receive a verification email or SMS to the 
            email address or phone number provided during registration. Click on the verification link in the email or follow the 
            instructions in the SMS to verify your account.
        </p><br>

        <h3>4. Profile Creation</h3> 
        <p>Once your account is verified, you will be prompted to complete your profile by providing additional information such as your location, preferences (if you're a buyer), or property details (if you're an owner). Completing your profile helps us match you with suitable properties or buyers efficiently.
        </p><br>
        
        <h3>5. Confirmation</h3>
        <p>After completing your profile, you will receive a confirmation message indicating that your registration is successful. You can now start using our platform to search for properties, list properties for sale or rent, and connect with potential tenants or buyers.
        </p><br>

        <h3>6. Important Information:</h3>
        <p>6.1.  Please ensure that the information provided during registration is accurate and up-to-date to facilitate smooth communication and transactions.</p>
        <p>6.2. By registering on our platform, you agree to abide by our Terms and Conditions, Service Fee Agreement, and Privacy Policy.</p>
        <p>6.3. If you have any questions or encounter any issues during the registration process, please contact our customer support team for assistance.</p><br>

        <h3></h3>
        <p>Thank you for choosing HOMEHUB AGENCY. We look forward to helping you find your dream property or connect with the perfect tenant or buyer.

        </p><br>         
